title: [SOLVED]820-3437-B no power
message:
Are you getting PP5V_S5?
L7520 seems to be powered by PP5V_S4RS3. If PP5V_S5 is missing then I dont think you would get P5VS4RS3 Have you checked the P5VS4RS3_EN on U7501?

I've only had a quick glance so I may be reading it completely wrong.

title: [SOLVED]820-3437-B no power
message:
PP5V_S5 : 5V
P5VS4RS3_EN_R on U7501 : 0V and pin 2 of U7501 P5VS4RS3 0V
